# Tactile Component Patterns

## Required Component Structure

### Typography Components
All text elements must follow the tactile typography hierarchy:

```tsx
// ✅ Headlines - Always use font-headline
<h1 className="font-headline text-charcoal text-4xl font-bold">
  Main Headline
</h1>

// ✅ Body text - Always use font-body
<p className="font-body text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
  Body content with proper opacity for hierarchy
</p>

// ❌ Never mix fonts inappropriately
<h1 className="font-body">Wrong Font</h1>
<p className="font-headline">Wrong Font</p>
```

### Interactive Elements
All interactive elements must use tactile styling:

```tsx
// ✅ Primary buttons
<button className="tactile-button">
  Primary Action
</button>

// ✅ Secondary buttons
<button className="tactile-button-secondary">
  Secondary Action
</button>

// ✅ Form inputs
<input 
  className="tactile-input w-full" 
  placeholder="Descriptive placeholder..."
/>

// ❌ Never use generic Tailwind button styles
<button className="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded">
  Generic Button
</button>
```

### Container Components
All container elements should use tactile card styling:

```tsx
// ✅ Card containers with tactile qualities
<div className="tactile-card paper-texture p-8">
  <h2 className="font-headline text-charcoal mb-4">Card Title</h2>
  <div className="space-y-4">
    {/* Card content */}
  </div>
</div>

// ✅ Section containers with background texture
<section className="bg-parchment bg-grain min-h-screen p-8">
  <div className="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    {/* Section content */}
  </div>
</section>

// ❌ Avoid generic white backgrounds and sharp corners
<div className="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
  <h2>Generic Card</h2>
</div>
```

## Component Composition Rules

### Color Usage
- **Backgrounds**: Always start with `bg-parchment` for main areas
- **Text**: Use `text-charcoal` for primary text, `text-charcoal/80` for secondary
- **Accents**: `bg-terracotta` for primary actions, `bg-sage` for secondary actions
- **Never**: Use pure white (`bg-white`) or pure black (`text-black`)

### Spacing and Layout
- **Padding**: Use generous padding (p-8, p-12) for breathing room
- **Margins**: Use consistent spacing with Tailwind's spacing scale
- **Max Width**: Constrain content with `max-w-4xl` or similar for readability

### State Management
Interactive elements must provide tactile feedback:

```tsx
// ✅ Proper hover and active states are built into tactile classes
<button className="tactile-button">
  {/* Hover: shadow-paper-lg, Active: shadow-paper-inner + translate */}
  Button with Tactile Feedback
</button>

// ✅ Form focus states
<input 
  className="tactile-input focus:border-sage focus:shadow-paper-inner" 
  onFocus={() => {/* Handle focus */}}
/>
```

## Anti-Patterns to Avoid

### ❌ Generic Material Design
```tsx
// Don't use sharp, geometric Material Design patterns
<Paper elevation={2}>
  <Button variant="contained" color="primary">
    Material Button
  </Button>
</Paper>
```

### ❌ Pure Minimalism
```tsx
// Avoid overly minimal, cold designs
<div className="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4">
  <h2 className="text-gray-900 text-lg">Minimal Card</h2>
</div>
```

### ❌ Inconsistent Typography
```tsx
// Never mix font families randomly
<div>
  <h1 className="font-sans">Sans Headline</h1>
  <p className="font-serif">Serif Body</p>
</div>
```

## Required Imports
Always import fonts properly in layout files:

```tsx
import { Inter, Playfair_Display } from "next/font/google";

const inter = Inter({
  variable: "--font-inter",
  subsets: ["latin"],
  display: "swap",
});

const playfairDisplay = Playfair_Display({
  variable: "--font-playfair", 
  subsets: ["latin"],
  display: "swap",
});
```